              <div class="field-items">
               <div class="field-item even">
                <h3>CaRDI</h3> 
                <p>Cornell University<br> 275 Warren Hall<br> Ithaca, NY 14853<br> Phone: (607) 255-9510<br> Fax: (607) 255-2231<br> Email: <a href="mailto:cardi@cornell.edu">cardi@cornell.edu</a></p> 
                <h3>Request Information</h3> 
                <p>If you would like to receive information disseminated by CaRDI, <strong><a href="https://jfe.qualtrics.com/form/SV_cZ1Lhqwa2XCdLVO">please fill out this form</a></strong>.</p> 
